race.description: Betdeluxe Con Sciacca Capalaba Cup Final (G2)
race.comment: SERIAL STICKER (6) recorded a win over 366m at this track in a head turning 19.53 last start. In form and can measure up again. MILES ON IT (4) will take beating coming off a scintillating 19.41 win at this track over 366m. Should be in this for a long way. BLUE BLEND (2) is a progressive type who recorded his 13th career win last time out (19.44) at this track. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of three tries. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. One of main contenders. SECRET STORY (8) placed last time (19.42) at this track in a OPEN, finishing second and beaten a nose. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.
